            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Harol! I made the missing parts!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "...I see. Alright, let me check them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Here you go!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Hm..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x25,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Um... Is it no good...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "...No, to be honest, I'm surprised. They're better made than I imagined."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "They're built even more precisely and elaborately than the ones engineers make."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Then..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, this is more than enough. I'll fix that box like you asked."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1a,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Yay! Thank you so much, Harol!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "There's no need to thank me. I'm half doing this out of my own personal interest."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Still, the internal structure is really precise. It'll take some time to fix it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I'll bring it over to your atelier when the repairs are done. Just sit tight and wait."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I understand! I'll leave it to you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x7,
            "name_id": 0x7,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, just leave it to me."
        }
    ]
}